data.description: Step into luxury living with this stunning 2017 Adams Home on nearly 2/3 of an acre nestled in the coveted Plantation Palms Subdivision. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a versatile office/den, Plus a salt water POOL, this home offers ample space for both relaxation and productivity. As you enter, you're greeted by an inviting open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying family time. The separate dining area adds a touch of elegance, while the beautiful kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, pantry, breakfast nook and tons of cabinets for storage. The master bedroom is a sanctuary unto itself, featuring not one, but two walk-in closets, and an in Suite bath with separate dual sinks, a separate bathtub, and shower for ultimate comfort and convenience. 3 additional bedrooms and 2 more full baths ensure plenty of accommodation options for family and guests alike. Step outside to your own private oasis, where a screened-in lanai awaits, overlooking a sparkling pool surrounded by meticulously landscaped grounds. Situated on a cul-de-sac, this home offers both privacy and tranquility, making it the perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home!  Upgrades galore with double hung windows, luxury vinyl plank and 18'' tile flooring, counter height vanities in all bathrooms, fiber optic and Spectrum internet and TV services available, underground utilities, septic serviced in last 6 months, regular pest control services, storage shed in the back and whole lawn irrigation.  Don't wait, homes this new with this much to offer on this amount of property are hard to come by at this price, schedule your showing today!
